data.description: Open  House Sunday 4/14/24 from 1:00 pm. - 3:00 pm. Beautiful brick colonial, recently converted to a 2 bedroom home.  A true gem features a semi-open floor plan that showcases hardwood flooring in the living room, dining room and bedrooms.  A spacious kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and tons of cabinet space.  The finished basement is  absolutely stunning and is great for entertaining or extra living space (refrigerator included) .  This home is situated on a double lot, with a fenced in yard and covered patio area offering plenty of room for hosting family gatherings and outdoor relaxation.  An extra long driveway and 2 car garage allows for plenty of parking.  This home has great curb appeal, nestled in the wonderful Wyandotte community that offers scenic waterfronts, and a vibrant downtown with boutiques, restaurants and entertainment.  Conveniently located near major freeways and shopping.  Home can easily be converted back to a 3 bedroom home.  The sellers have completed the city inspection  and the Certificate of Approval has been issued.
